OL,3,CPoundland to shut 68 shops and two
OL,4,Cwarehouses after takeover
OL,6,FHundreds of jobs are at risk at
OL,7,FPoundland after the retailer announced
OL,8,Fplans to shut 68 shops and two of its
OL,9,FUK warehouses following its takeover
OL,10,Fby investment firm Gordon Brothers.
OL,12,FLast week, Pepco Group sold the
OL,13,Fdiscount chain for #1 after it had
OL,14,Fbeen hit by a sharp downturn in
OL,15,Ftrading in recent years.
OL,17,FOn Tuesday, Poundland said it is
OL,18,Fseeking court approval for a
OL,19,Frestructuring plan to shut 68 shops
OL,20,Fand secure rent reductions on dozens
OL,21,Fmore.
