OL,3,CPoundland to shut 68 shops and two
OL,4,Cwarehouses after takeover
OL,6,FThe retailer said it expects to end up
OL,7,Fwith between 650 and 700 stores after
OL,8,Fthe overhaul. It currently runs around
OL,9,F800 stores across the UK and Ireland
OL,10,Fbut stressed Irish shops have not been
OL,11,Faffected.
OL,13,FPoundland said it also plans to close
OL,14,Fits frozen and digital distribution
OL,15,Fsite at Darton, South Yorkshire, later
OL,16,Fthis year and another warehouse at
OL,17,FSpringvale in Bilston, West Midlands,
OL,18,Fin early 2026.
OL,20,FAround 350 people will be affected by
OL,21,Fthe warehouse closures.
